<br>
With the new damage bonuses on slow two-hand weapons, the gap has narrowed significantly. Even high-end rangers, the die-hard dual-wielders are starting to move towards two-handers in certain circumstances.<br>
<br>
Obviously, the best thing is to carry both and learn which works best against which creatures. Remember also, that as a tank, you are taking reposts and the slower weapons mean less HP loss (similar logic applies to damage shields).<br>
<br>
